"signal_description": "The SIGNAL query is calculating the average time difference between two events in the 'defaultview-57' table. The first event is the last occurrence of 'Clear Invoice' and the second event is the first occurrence of either 'Record Invoice Receipt' or 'Create FI Invoice'. The time of these events is recorded in the 'end_time' column. The query first selects the 'end_time' of the last 'Clear Invoice' event, then subtracts from it the 'end_time' of the first 'Record Invoice Receipt' or 'Create FI Invoice' event. The average of these time differences is then calculated."
}
